    <summary>Kotlin-native DSL for UML, SysML 2, and C4 diagrams — type-safe, versionable, LLM-ready.</summary>
    <description>kUML is a Kotlin-native DSL for UML, SysML 2, and C4 architecture diagrams.

Models are plain Kotlin scripts: type-safe, refactorable, diff-friendly, and trivially
generated by LLMs. The `kuml` CLI renders diagrams to SVG/PNG, validates models,
formats them canonically, and embeds them in Markdown.

This package ships a self-contained build: a bundled Java 21 runtime is included,
so **no separate JDK installation is required**.

* Homepage: https://kuml.dev
* Source:   https://github.com/kuml-dev/kuml
* License:  Apache-2.0</description>
    <tags>kuml uml sysml c4 kotlin diagram modeling architecture cli developer-tools admin</tags>
